OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782733687
OL,3,CBody of teenage boy, 15, recovered
OL,4,Cfrom water
OL,6,FThe body of a teenage boy has been
OL,7,Frecovered from a reservoir in Tameside.
OL,9,FIt follows a huge emergency services
OL,10,Fresponse around Cowbury Reservoir in
OL,11,FStalybridge on Saturday evening.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police, in a
OL,14,Fstatement issued on Sunday 28 June,
OL,15,Fsaid emergency services were called to
OL,16,Freports of a 15 year-old boy getting
OL,17,Finto difficulty in the water at the
OL,18,Freservoir on Saturday 27 June. His
OL,19,Fbody was sadly later recovered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
