OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782733687
OL,3,CBody of teenage boy, 15, recovered
OL,4,Cfrom water
OL,6,FIn a statement, GMP said of the
OL,7,Ftragedy in Stalybridge: "At around
OL,8,F6.30pm police were called and
OL,9,Femergency service colleagues from
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService and North West Ambulance
OL,12,FService attended.
OL,14,F"Sadly, a body was located in the
OL,15,Fwater later that evening and was
OL,16,Frecovered by specialist partners.
OL,17,FFormal identification has taken place
OL,18,Fand his family have been made aware.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782733687
OL,3,CBody of teenage boy, 15, recovered
OL,4,Cfrom water
OL,6,F"Detectives from Tameside CID are ` at
OL,7,Fthis stage ` confident that there
OL,8,Faren't any suspicious circumstances,
OL,9,Fand a file is being prepared for the
OL,10,Fcoroner."
OL,12,FTameside Chief Inspector Helen Baxter
OL,13,Fsaid: "Yesterday's events are nothing
OL,14,Fshort of devastating and my thoughts
OL,15,Fare with the family and loved ones of
OL,16,Fthe young boy who sadly lost his life
OL,17,Fin such awful circumstances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782733687
OL,3,CBody of teenage boy, 15, recovered
OL,4,Cfrom water
OL,6,F"We are confident that there are no
OL,7,Fsuspicious circumstances and that this
OL,8,Fis such a sad reminder of the dangers
OL,9,Fof entering open water. We remind the
OL,10,Fpublic to please avoid being tempted
OL,11,Fto cool off in reservoirs, rivers,
OL,12,Fcanals or ponds.
OL,14,F"We all want to enjoy the warm
OL,15,Fweather; please make sure you do so in
OL,16,Fa safe way."
OL,18,FThe news brings the total number of
OL,19,Fdrownings across the country during
OL,20,Fthe recent heatwave to seven.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
